{{Infobox person | name = Sherman Kwek | image = | image_size = | caption = | birth_name = Eik Tse Kwek | birth_date = {{birth based on age as of date |42|2018|01|02}}<ref name="Bloomberg profile"/> | birth_place = | death_date = | death_place = | death_cause = | nationality = Singaporean | residence = Singapore | education = | alma mater = [[Boston University]] | occupation = | title = CEO, City Developments Limited | term = | predecessor = | successor = | known for = | boards = | salary = | networth = | spouse = | children = | parents = [[Kwek Leng Beng]] | relations = | website = }}
'''Eik Tse "Sherman" Kwek''' (born 1975/76) is a Singaporean businessman, and the CEO of City Developments Limited since January 2018.
Sherman Kwek earned a bachelor's degree in business administration from [[Boston University]].<ref name="Bloomberg profile">{{cite web|title=Executive Profile: Eik Tse Kwek|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/research/stocks/people/person.asp?personId=28282753&privcapId=8081299|website=Bloomberg LP|accessdate=2 January 2018}}</ref>
In August 2017, Kwek, then deputy CEO, became CEO-designate after the then CEO [[Grant Kelley]] resigned after three and a half years in the role, and left at the end of 2017.<ref name="auto">{{cite web|url=http://www.straitstimes.com/business/companies-markets/cdl-names-sherman-kwek-ceo-designate-with-resignation-of-grant-kelley-q2|title=CDL names Sherman Kwek CEO-designate with resignation of Grant Kelley, Q2 profit falls 17.9%|first=|last=hermesauto|date=11 August 2017|publisher=|accessdate=2 January 2018}}</ref><ref name="mingtiandi.com">{{cite web|url=https://www.mingtiandi.com/real-estate/agencies-people/sherman-kwek-replacing-grant-kelley-as-cdl-chief-executive/|title=Sherman Kwek Replaces Grant Kelley as CDL's CEO - Mingtiandi|website=www.mingtiandi.com|accessdate=2 January 2018}}</ref>
In January 2018, he became the CEO of City Developments Limited.<ref name="auto"/><ref name="mingtiandi.com"/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://sg.asiatatler.com/tatler-list/300list/sherman-kwek|title=Sherman Kwek Profile - Singapore Tatler|website=Singapore Tatler|accessdate=2 January 2018}}</ref>
